casebody.data:
Teressa B. ROUSE
v.
FORSYTH COUNTY DEPARTMENT OF SOCIAL SERVICES No. 1PA19 Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 9, 2019 Gloria L. Woods, Assistant County Attorney, For Forsyth County Department of Social Services Benjamin P. Winikoff, Attorney at Law, For Rouse, Teressa B. Gloria L. Woods, Assistant County Attorney

ORDER

Upon consideration of the conditional petition filed on the 11th of January 2019 by Respondent in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 9th of May 2019."
